// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3267 — Mass File Rename (ransomhouse)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: afe28f53-e662-532b-863b-ca51afa28cf4

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
